{"title":"诗二首　扶同志上悬崖","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶同志上悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的心眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀好心眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌也难唱完；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她扶的同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上盘松的山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘松山上："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一丈高的悬崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比是铁板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在半空间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“敌人烧村了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快踩上我的肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬上这悬崖。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤员就答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“眼看这悬崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上也不行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不上也不沾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片刻间、戎冠秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁花怒开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她弯下腰拍拍肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志上我的肩。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崖上有个洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也高也秘密；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（她事先找的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何人都不知。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要上了崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于船靠了岸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖象铁板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在盘松山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎冠秀象铁花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开在盘松山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是好同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好同志，你好比河里水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上亮晶晶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有功劳不吹牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有缺点就纠正。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你好比那河里的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜，时时刻刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向大海流去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不愿停在死水坑。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}